The old DiskSafe Release 1.03 was broken due to a bug in the Fast File
System (Thanx, C= :-( ).


The "complete test" of the 1.11 and earlier releases has proven to be not
very relyable. Please run the @{"new one" link Test} again.


The LOGFile option of 1.12 did not work properly on computers with no
autoconfig expansion RAM and FastExec, please update to 1.17!


